com.interpss.core.dclf

Interface IBranchAngleShiftFactor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    DclfAlgorithm
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DclfAlgorithmImpl

    public interface IBranchAngleShiftFactor
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'IBranch Angle Shift Factor'. calculate network loss factor with one inject bus and one or many withdraw bus(es) by injecting a 1.0pu current into the injection bus and withdraw the current from the the withdraw bus(es).
    See Also:
    DclfPackage.getIBranchAngleShiftFactor()
